    "description": "The Cyberflex Access 64K V2 with PKI applets provides secure PKI (public key infrastructure) and digital signature technology. Cyberflex Access 64K V2 serves as a highly portable, secure device for enhancing the security of network access and ensuring secure electronic communications. Cyberflex Access 64K V2 supports on-card Triple-DES, AES and 2048-bit RSA algorithms with on-card key generation. It is compliant to Java Card v2.1.1 and Open Platform v2.0.1. The Cyberflex Access 64K V2 smart card fits well into physical and logical access, e-transactions and other applications.",
